[[File:Lupror-CaptainPhasma2.png|thumb|right|300px|[[Lupr'or]] colonists]]
A '''colonist''', also known as a '''settler''', was an individual who migrated as part of a group that sought to exercise power over their area of colonization. Early colonists of the [[planet]] [[Tatooine]] were drawn by the promise of [[mining]] the [[desert]] planet's mineral wealth and were forced to adapt to its harsh environment, using [[moisture vaporator]]s to gather as much [[water]] as possible from the world's parched [[atmosphere]]. [[Human]] colonists on the planet they named [[Naboo]] competed with the [[Homeworld|native]] [[Gungan]]s, threatening the [[Sentience|sentients']] [[Symbiosis|symbiotic]] relationship with the natural environment and setting up a separate [[Naboo (people)|Naboo]] culture based in the [[capital]] [[city]] [[Theed]].<ref name="CL 2016">[[Star Wars: Complete Locations (2016)|''Star Wars: Complete Locations'']]</ref>

Colonists sometimes traveled to planets they colonized aboard [[colony ship]]s.<ref name="CL 2016" />

